      <p class="text-text-muted text-sm mb-10">Last updated: April 23, 2026</p>

      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
        Please read these terms and conditions carefully before using Our Service.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Communications</h2>
      <p class="text-text-muted text-lg leading-relaxed mb-8">
        When you visit <a href="https://rankinwaste.com/" class="text-orange-500 hover:text-orange-300 transition-colors duration-300">https://rankinwaste.com/</a> or send e-emails to us, you are communicating with us electronically. You consent to receive communications from us electronically. We will communicate with you by email through your Rankin Waste Management workspaces or by posting notices on this site. You agree that all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications that we provide to you electronically satisfy any legal requirement that such communications be in writing.
